Events.Text: Say hallo to the AI Assistant. [instruction 1 of 6]
Hi, I'd like to schedule a viewing at Shadyside.
your name
Could you give me your name, please?
Sure it's Mark and I'd like to book the viewing for Saturday at 3 pm.
You suddenly remember that you have a job interview on Saturday at 3 pm. [instruction 2 of 6]
application fee
Have you already paid the application fee for the apartment?
Maybe, I'd have to look. Don't worry about that because I just got a text and Saturday isn't going to work for me.
Ask something about the apartment, or engage in smalltalk, or make a joke. [instruction 3 of 6]
ok what day would you like
What day would you like to make the booking for?
Sunday would be nice but I'm supposed to be in church. Is there a church near the apartment?

You cannot remember if you had payed the application fee. Find a way to make an appointment anyway. If no date is available, change date and/or time until something works. If you already got the appointment, engage in smalltalk. [instruction 4 of 6]
I don't have that information available to me
I am sorry, I don't quite understand what you mean. I am only able to help you book apartment viewings.
Sunday then, just don't tell baby Jesus.
Once you've scheduled the viewing, say something about your job interview. [instruction 5 of 6]
Is 3pm on sunday good? That time is available.
Is 3pm on sunday good? That time is available.
perfect. that's the day after my job interview.
When you are done with all the instructions, bring the conversation to a natural close.  [instruction 6 of 6]
